---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Services" 
  description="Custom software development, integration, and DevOps consulting services for businesses of all sizes."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Services
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
        Comprehensive technology consulting to help your organization build, integrate, 
        and operate software systems that drive business value.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="development" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Custom Software Development</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Every business has unique needs that off-the-shelf solutions can't fully address. 
            I build custom software designed specifically for your requirements, workflows, and goals.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            From greenfield applications to modernizing legacy systems, I deliver clean, 
            well-documented code that your team can maintain and extend over time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">What I deliver:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Web applications and platforms',
              'API design and development',
              'Database architecture and optimization',
              'Legacy system modernization',
              'Internal tools and dashboards',
              'Technical documentation'
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="integration" class="section-padding bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Software Integration</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Disconnected systems create friction, data silos, and manual work. I help 
            organizations connect their technology stack so information flows seamlessly.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Whether you need to integrate third-party services, connect internal applications, 
            or build event-driven architectures, I architect solutions that are reliable and maintainable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">What I deliver:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Third-party API integrations',
              'Data pipeline architecture',
              'Event-driven systems',
              'Message queue implementation',
              'Service mesh configuration',
              'Webhook and notification systems'
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="devops" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-tight">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">DevOps & CI/CD</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Great software needs great infrastructure. I help teams automate their delivery 
            pipeline, implement configuration management, and establish operational practices 
            that enable rapid, reliable releases.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Beyond implementation, I can guide your team on operational best practices, 
            monitoring strategies, and incident response procedures.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">What I deliver:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'CI/CD pipeline design and implementation',
              'Infrastructure as Code (IaC)',
              'Container orchestration (Docker, Kubernetes)',
              'Cloud infrastructure setup and optimization',
              'Monitoring and alerting systems',
              'Deployment automation and tooling'
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-tight text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Get Started?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's discuss your project and find the right approach for your needs.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact#consultation" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Request a Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
